(70, 'SATRIA', 'satria', '<p style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"http://gerindra.anakbangsa.xyz/asset/images/file_1611523821.jpg\" style=\"width: 180px;\"></p><div style=\"font-family: Gotham-Book; font-size: 14px;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#222222\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">SEJARAH</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</span></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Satuan Relawan\r\nIndonesia Raya ( SATRIA) di dirikan di jakarta pada tanggal 30 Mei 2008. Pada\r\nawalnya adalah sebagai satuan tugas ( SATGAS ) partai GERINDRA.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Dalam perjalananya\r\nGERINDRA menyadari bahwa dibutuhkan satu organisasi sayap sebagai sumber resources\r\nkader partai, sehingga peran SATRIA saat ini adalah sebagai sumber kader\r\npartai.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Helvetica;\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Hingga saat ini SATRIA\r\nmenjadi organisasi sayap partai Gerakan Indonesia Raya (GERINDRA) yg berjuang\r\ndemi tegaknya Pancasila, UUD 1945 dan Utuhnya Negara Kesatuan Republik\r\nIndonesia.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Helvetica;\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><br></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#222222\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">HIRARKI</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Helvetica;\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#222222\"=\"\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Hubungan Pimpinan\r\nPusat SATRIA dengan Dewan Pimpinan Pusat Partai GERINDRA adalah hirarki yang\r\nbersifat instruktif. Sedangkan Hubungan Organisasi Pimpinan Daerah SATRIA\r\nsampai ke tingkat bawah dengan Partai GERINDRA adalah bersifat koordinatif dan\r\nmenempatkan Ketua Partai di masing-masing tingkatan sebagai Ketua Dewan\r\nPenasehat SATRIA sesuai dengan tingkatanya. Sementara hubungan Pimpinan Pusat\r\nSATRIA, Pimpinan Daerah, Pimpinan Cabang, Pimpinan Anak Cabang adalah\r\ninstruktif.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Helvetica;\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><br></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#222222\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">TUGAS SATRIA</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Helvetica;\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#222222\"=\"\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Tugas SATRIA\r\nmenghimpun, menggalang, mengembangkan dan meningkatkan sumber daya dan potensi\r\nmasyarakat dalam upaya mewujudkan cita-cita nasional bangsa Indonesia yang\r\nadil, makmur dan sejahtera serta membantu penanggulangan bencana nasional dalam\r\nsegi sosial.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Helvetica;\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">SATRIA mengawal\r\npemenangan partai GERINDRA dan bisa berperan dalam penyelenggaraan Negara yang\r\njujur, berkualitas, berdaya guna dalam lingkup Pancasila dan UUD 1945. Sebagai\r\norganisasi sayap Partai GERINDRA, SATRIA memiliki basis nasa di kalangan\r\npemuda. SATRIA adalah organisasi sayap Partai Gerindra yang menjaring\r\nmasyarakat yang hendak membantu sesama secara sukarela, terutama dalam\r\npenanggulangan bencana.&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\"><br></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; background: rgb(252, 252, 252); color: rgb(54, 54, 53); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; background: rgb(252, 252, 252); color: rgb(54, 54, 53); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\"><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; background: transparent;\">PENGURUS PUSAT (PP) SATRIA</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; background: rgb(252, 252, 252); color: rgb(54, 54, 53); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; background: rgb(252, 252, 252); color: rgb(54, 54, 53); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\"><b 